  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_019b33159126329b03c40fbad7131333">
    <head>Content Description</head>
<p>The James Cunningham photographs (1968-1973) contains photographs, contact sheets, and negatives taken by James Cunningham during his time as a student at Cornell University. Photographs include candids of students, Cornell Athletics games, campus events, and campus scenes.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <bioghist audience="internal" id="aspace_07329f3de0de848bb891db4fa3542e63">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>James Cunningham graduated from Cornell University in 1971.</p>  </bioghist>
